metadata.name: WEN AL
metadata.description:
If you're not in AL, you're the EXIT STRATEGY.

Meme derivative of EXIT STRATEGY by XCOPY, Meme card #47.

From 6529: "The Memes Collection is focused on the fight for the open metaverse (decentralization, community, self-sovereignty) and spreading this message to many people, many wallets. We will try to have a good time along the way, make some fun art...and just generally have a good time."
